Charlie Musselwhite - Juke Joint Chapel (2013) FLAC 

Legendary Charlie Musselwhite backed by his acclaimed kick ass band - rocking' the house! With his latest release, Juke Joint Chapel, blues harpist and vocalist Charlie Musselwhite has compiled an impressive release full of five originals and seven covers.
